  "keyFeatures": [
    "116 MCP tools across 17 categories for Oracle APEX 24.2 development",
    "High-level generators for CRUD, dashboards, analytics pages, wizards, and REST endpoints",
    "Supports Claude, GPT, Gemini, Cursor, VS Code, and any MCP-compatible AI client",
    "Three transport modes: stdio, streamable-HTTP, and SSE",
    "Connects to Oracle Autonomous Database via oracledb thin driver with mTLS wallet (no Instant Client)",
    "Batch mode and dry-run mode for safe, efficient app creation",
    "20 rich HTML UI components and 10 advanced chart types",
    "MCP resources and workflow prompts for guided app building",
    "Full schema introspection with FK relationship detection",
    "App export, page diffing, Markdown doc generation, and ORDS REST endpoint generation"
  ],
